
part ::= id, property*

property ∈ { price, amount, ... }

## create new part [by providing a complete document]

POST /v/parts

====> /v/parts/{id}

## { create, retrieve, update, delete } { part, part property }

{VERB} /v/parts/{id}

====> part [object, e.g. JSON]

{VERB} /v/parts/{id}/properties/{property-name}

====> property value [value, e.g. JSON value]

with
  {property-name} ∈ { price, location, ... }
  {VERB} ∈ { GET, PUT, DELETE }

where
  GET = retrieve part [property]
  PUT = { create, update} part [property]
  DELETE = delete part [property]

Note: POST /v/parts is similar PUT /v/parts/{new-id}

## search parts

GET /v/methods/search?fulltext={query}

====> ...

## 

POST /v/parts/{id}/properties/{property-name}/methods/{method-name}

